    ...    tedge flows test --base64-output te/device/main///m/env '{"time":"2025-06-27T08:11:05.301804125Z", "temperature": 258}'
    ...    strip=True
    Should Be Equal
    ...    ${transformed_msg}
    ...    [c8y/measurement/measurements/create] ${encoded_output}

